				\begin{document}$$d_{C}$$\end{document}dC denotes the position of this transition of behaviour in number of days elapsed since the beginning of the data set, i.e. 14 March 2020. We have denoted this day as a critical day \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
